{"tid":1360281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出老解兩岸和平統一就推遲一百年","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:45:13.000Z","uid":4161,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88de17158d38fa8ed98e4f5622232bf2a260a1dc","tid":1360281,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"出到靠嚇證明無招喇<br />\n出老解台灣仲俾你統一?<br />\n武統老解打得贏美日台?<br />\n<br />\n香港係大陸眼中只係一粒塵<br />\n台灣先係最重要<br />\n最緊要係俾到示範台灣人統一既好處<br />\n柒婆已經攪到蔡英文翻身<br />\n出埋老解就唔使旨意和平統一<br />\n<br />\n呢條數咁簡單係香港人都識計啦<br />\n信你會出就奇<br />\n<br />\n利申覺得可惜本來想早日共享大灣區榮耀"},{"pid":"fdaf9100186e5facb6f34dc7cff967ed2a175eb8","tid":1360281,"uid":42149,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"諗都知冇可能。<br />\n出老解trump 借啲耳發鳩維尼脾氣，搞鳩佢<br />\n台灣見到咁，又更加冇可能接管台灣。<br />\n台灣發大財，命都冇點發"},{"pid":"5e4130da6b76cfa4eeef365266e386c7911348bc","tid":1360281,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n個個ＰＯＳＴ都係老解老解！<br />\n有冇Ｄ新意呀！<br />\n臨時演員都係演員啦，俾Ｄ精神！<br />\n<br />\n你地支那人驚姐，香港人唔驚架！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"65452c490d447f3eec0646a30dc207424fad75a2","tid":1360281,"uid":286958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"005824321f0116d541bb56df00ef514cf755597a","tid":1360281,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edf00d9df9a82e02f30e4c469ef10f68cb11f216","tid":1360281,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"一早已經冇可能和平統一"},{"pid":"799b2de04c967d21121c13d397d6a318d2e2cb63","tid":1360281,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"005824321f0116d541bb56df00ef514cf755597a","tid":1360281,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:23:4